1
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:50,200
Something's wrong.

2
00:00:51,039 --> 00:00:51,759
Lao Jiugui!

3
00:00:52,719 --> 00:00:53,439
Where are the Ghost Soldiers?

4
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:54,679
There are no Ghost Soldiers!

5
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:57,719
Chuanzhong,

6
00:00:58,399 --> 00:01:00,079
spin around twice,

7
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:02,640
then look again.

8
00:01:03,159 --> 00:01:03,560
This...

9
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:08,159
There they are!

10
00:01:08,519 --> 00:01:09,359
They're coming!

11
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:18,040
That's my position!

12
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:19,959
Why did you summon the Ghost Soldiers

13
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:21,159
to my own position?

14
00:01:21,359 --> 00:01:22,560
Then where should I summon them?

15
00:01:23,439 --> 00:01:25,200
To the opposite side, of course!

16
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,319
You...

17
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,120
You did it on purpose!

18
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,519
Looks to me

19
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:36,840
like you want your disciples dead!

20
00:01:38,359 --> 00:01:39,120
What are you doing?

21
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,480
So many ghosts!

22
00:01:43,719 --> 00:01:44,439
So many ghosts!

23
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:46,920
More ghosts are coming!

24
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:48,359
More ghosts are coming!

25
00:01:48,879 --> 00:01:49,599
More ghosts are coming!

26
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,319
Zhou Xingbang!

27
00:01:50,319 --> 00:01:50,799
Are you okay?

28
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:51,680
You traitor!

29
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:42,919
Qiuying,

30
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,000
put down your weapons,

31
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,120
and I'll let you off.

32
00:02:47,719 --> 00:02:50,080
That's what I should be saying to you.

33
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:52,960
My sister and brother-in-law are gone.

34
00:02:53,319 --> 00:02:55,080
I'm the only family you have left.

35
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,960
I am now

36
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,199
the mayor of Yinyang Crossing.

37
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,479
How about this?

38
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,199
When the commander returns,

39
00:03:04,759 --> 00:03:06,199
I'll put in a good word for Shuisheng,

40
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,360
so he can, like me,

41
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:10,080
become

42
00:03:10,719 --> 00:03:11,759
the chief of police.

43
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:12,759
Wouldn't that be nice?

44
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,319
Shut up!

45
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,840
You don't deserve to be my uncle!

46
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,120
Your damn commander isn't coming back!

47
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,120
What?

48
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:24,360
You should've been burned at the ritual.

49
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,439
Tell me,

50
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,080
did you kill my mother?

51
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,560
Her bones have long been buried.

52
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,080
Master,

53
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,319
what's going on here?

54
00:03:42,199 --> 00:03:45,400
Li Chuanzhong's coveted Ghost Soldiers.

55
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:48,599
Do Ghost Soldiers really exist?

56
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:49,120
Master,

57
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,360
I'd like to know too.

58
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:52,240
Brother,

59
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:53,560
are you alright?

60
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:54,120
I'm fine.

61
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:55,599
Shuisheng and Qiuying saved me.

62
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:58,159
It was Master's brilliant plan.

63
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,479
He knew once the fighting started here,

64
00:03:59,479 --> 00:04:00,599
Yinyang Crossing would be left undefended.

65
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:01,599
Master,

66
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,639
what exactly are these Ghost Soldiers?

67
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,439
Ghosts don't even exist in this world.

68
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,000
How could there be Ghost Soldiers?

69
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,000
They

70
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:13,560
ate this.

71
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:15,159
Mushrooms?

72
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:21,360
Who's there?

73
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:23,199
Me, me, me!

74
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:23,720
Me!

75
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,120
I don't know you!

76
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:28,040
I'm just a mushroom picker.

77
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:30,279
Come here!

78
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,079
Come here!

79
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,199
Help me dig wild greens.

80
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:35,000
Dig wild greens?

81
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:39,399
But don't they say

82
00:04:39,519 --> 00:04:41,600
soldiers eat and drink the best?

83
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,920
Why are you digging wild greens?

84
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,600
That's only the officers.

85
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:48,920
For us,

86
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:51,240
wild greens and mushrooms are already a treat.

87
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:52,959
Hurry up and dig.

88
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:56,759
But I still need to go sell my mushrooms.

89
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:58,519
If I

90
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,560
can't get down the mountain,

91
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,879
and the mushrooms don't get sold,

92
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:02,720
tomorrow there'll be no...

93
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:05,399
Why not just sell the mushrooms to me?

94
00:05:06,439 --> 00:05:07,240
That'd be wonderful!

95
00:05:08,439 --> 00:05:09,160
That'd be wonderful!

96
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:10,600
Wonderful!

97
00:05:13,439 --> 00:05:14,000
Alright.

98
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:18,720
But you're holding me.

99
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,720
How am I supposed to pay you?

100
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:34,160
Give me your hand.

101
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:38,639
No, wait.

102
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:39,199
I...

103
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:40,800
I don't smoke.

104
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,279
My mushrooms!

105
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:43,000
My mushrooms!

106
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:43,879
Don't run!

107
00:05:44,199 --> 00:05:45,920
Stop running!

108
00:05:48,439 --> 00:05:50,560
So the commander and his men ate these?

109
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:51,639
That's right.

110
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:54,360
Serve the soup.

111
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:55,959
Everyone, time to eat!

112
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,279
Come on, come on.

113
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:04,480
They just...

114
00:06:05,399 --> 00:06:06,720
ate these mushrooms.

115
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,439
Children.

116
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:11,839
Your master...

117
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:14,079
has nothing left to teach you now.

118
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,319
The road ahead...

119
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,480
you must walk on your own.

120
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:22,199
All I can do is wish you...

121
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,920
a smooth journey.

122
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:25,439
Now go.

123
00:06:27,319 --> 00:06:27,959
Xiaolian.

124
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:29,120
I'm going with you.

125
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:31,600
Comrade Dongsheng.

126
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:34,040
Your Party application is approved.

127
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,040
Congratulations.

128
00:06:35,319 --> 00:06:35,959
Really?

129
00:06:36,319 --> 00:06:37,199
That's wonderful!

130
00:06:39,199 --> 00:06:39,759
Then...

131
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,759
can we join the ranks too?

132
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,680
You won't hold our background against us?

133
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:45,959
Of course not.

134
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,439
We couldn't be happier to have you.

135
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:51,480
Everyone's here today.

136
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,839
How about coming to Jigu Temple?

137
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:54,519
I'll cook you all a big meal.

138
00:06:55,839 --> 00:06:57,240
There's no time.

139
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,199
Let's go.

140
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,439
Time to hit the road.

141
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,399
Master.

142
00:07:06,279 --> 00:07:07,360
Aren't you happy?

143
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,120
I am happy.

144
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:13,600
I couldn't be happier.

145
00:07:15,199 --> 00:07:17,160
I'll be waiting for news of your victory.

146
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,079
Now go.

147
00:07:20,199 --> 00:07:20,720
Master.

148
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:21,639
Auntie Xiaoling.

149
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:22,759
We're heading off now.

150
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,000
Goodbye.

151
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,759
Dongsheng.

152
00:07:31,639 --> 00:07:32,399
Xiaolian.

153
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,920
Remember to write!

154
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:37,560
Master, we're going.

155
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,120
Dongsheng!

156
00:07:45,439 --> 00:07:46,319
Don't call them back.

157
00:07:46,879 --> 00:07:47,839
Let them go.

158
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,040
What happened?

159
00:07:52,399 --> 00:07:53,319
I got shot.

160
00:07:58,959 --> 00:08:00,360
Help me back to Jigu Temple.

161
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,959
I dreamed about the kids.

162
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,199
Dongsheng...

163
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,559
and Xiaolian.

164
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,559
Have they written?

165
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,120
Yes, they have.

166
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,519
They say...

167
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,159
they've joined the regular army.

168
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:46,080
A big battle is coming soon.

169
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:48,519
After they win...

170
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,840
they'll come back to see us.

171
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:56,480
Good.

172
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:00,240
A big battle's coming...

173
00:09:01,519 --> 00:09:03,600
which means victory's not far off.

174
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:09,399
As long as the kids...

175
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,879
are safe and sound,

176
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:14,000
I'll be content.

177
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:18,759
Ruling.

178
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,559
I've let you down.

179
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,240
I made you stay in this temple of bones,

180
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:33,519
to keep me company,

181
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,559
to take care of me,

182
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,440
and to put up with me.

183
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,000
You silly Lao Jiugui.

184
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,799
Why bring all that up now?

185
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:56,879
You've grown old too.

186
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,519
Are you complaining I've gotten old?

187
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,000
When I was born,

188
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,399
you weren't yet born.

189
00:10:14,799 --> 00:10:15,879
By the time you were born,

190
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:20,000
I had already grown old.

191
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,720
I've wronged you.

192
00:10:31,039 --> 00:10:32,440
I'm so sorry.

193
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:39,000
I was always destined for a hard life.

194
00:10:40,519 --> 00:10:42,320
You're the one who saved me.

195
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,240
You gave me hope to keep living.

196
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:49,720
I'm willing to stay here at Jigu Temple,

197
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:54,639
to tend the eternal lamp for a lifetime.

198
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,519
There's no need.

199
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:12,360
Because our country now

200
00:11:13,879 --> 00:11:16,120
has a lamp that will never go out.

201
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:20,440
It will light our way

202
00:11:21,159 --> 00:11:23,080
on the path to happiness.

203
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:25,720
The good days

204
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,440
are coming very soon.

205
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:33,000
But I won't be around to see them.

206
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:43,919
Ruling.

207
00:11:46,759 --> 00:11:48,080
Do you still remember

208
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,159
the first time

209
00:11:52,759 --> 00:11:54,600
the two of us ever met?

210
00:11:57,799 --> 00:11:58,440
I remember.

211
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,759
Back then, I pretended to be a ghost,

212
00:12:02,399 --> 00:12:03,960
dancing around to scare you.

213
00:12:09,399 --> 00:12:10,240
Could you

214
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:14,879
dance for me one more time?

215
00:13:21,519 --> 00:13:22,320
You filthy old rascal!

216
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:23,399
What are you grabbing my chest for?

217
00:13:23,639 --> 00:13:24,559
And to think people

218
00:13:24,559 --> 00:13:26,159
say you're the reincarnation of Yama.

219
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,960
Thank you, Lao Jiugui.

220
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,840
I've put you through a lot, Ruling.

221
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,600
It wasn't just up to me.

222
00:13:33,919 --> 00:13:34,519
Eat the scallion.

223
00:13:34,759 --> 00:13:35,200
Eat.

224
00:13:35,279 --> 00:13:35,679
Go on, eat it.

225
00:13:35,919 --> 00:13:36,360
Eat.

226
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,120
Tell me,

227
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:17,559
after taking that pill,

228
00:14:18,039 --> 00:14:19,440
what happens if no one wakes you?

229
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:21,960
Then you sleep peacefully forever.

230
00:14:22,759 --> 00:14:24,519
Then I want to keep one too.

231
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:26,679
What for?

232
00:14:27,759 --> 00:14:29,799
What if you go before me?

233
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:30,919
No way.

234
00:14:31,879 --> 00:14:33,159
I'll definitely die before you.

235
00:14:34,759 --> 00:14:35,519
Don't jinx it.
